    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.142,
                0.545,
                0.242
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "二维离散型随机向量"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.084,
                0.304,
                0.923,
                0.468
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "已知 \\(P\\left(X = x_{i}, Y = y_{j}\\right) = p_{ij}, i = 1, \\ldots, I; j = 1, \\ldots, J\\) 。根据以上概率分布抽取 100 个样本。"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.082,
                0.594,
                0.923,
                0.896
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "把数据矩阵“拉直”为一个向量，即令 \\(P(Z = k) = P\\big(X = x_{i}, Y = y_{j}\\big), k = 1,2,\\ldots,I \\times J\\)，并记此概率为 \\(\\tilde{p}_{k}\\)。然后按照离散型随机变量的方式抽取100个 \\(Z\\) 的样本，并把 \\(k\\) 对应回 \\(x_{i}\\) 和 \\(y_{j}\\) 即可。"
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.146,
                0.543,
                0.236
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "二维离散型随机向量"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.3,
                0.611,
                0.36
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "\\(>\\mathrm{x}<-\\mathrm{c}(\\ldots);\\mathrm{y}<-\\mathrm{c}(\\ldots);\\mathrm{l}<-\\mathrm{length}(\\mathrm{x});\\mathrm{J}<-\\mathrm{length}(\\mathrm{y})\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.409,
                0.45,
                0.463
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "> \\(p<-matrix(..., nrow=1, ncol=J)\\)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.509,
                0.668,
                0.567
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "> p2<-as.vector(p) #注：按列拉直"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.616,
                0.672,
                0.672
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "> index<-sample(1:(I*J), 100, replace=T, prob=p2)"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.721,
                0.71,
                0.774
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "> index1<- (index-1)%%|+1; index2<- (index-1)%%|+1"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.826,
                0.604,
                0.881
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "> data_sample<-cbind(x[index1], y[index2])"
        },
        {
            "type": "list",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.3,
                0.71,
                0.881
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": null
        }
    ],
    [
        {
            "type": "title",
            "bbox": [
                0.097,
                0.142,
                0.545,
                0.239
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "二维离散型随机向量"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.084,
                0.294,
                0.923,
                0.46
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "1. 计算 \\(X\\) 的边缘概率，并记为 \\(p_{i + }\\) 。按照 \\(p_{i + }\\) 的概率从 \\(x_{i}\\) 中抽取 100 个样本，记为 \\(x_{1}^{*}, \\ldots, x_{100}^{*}\\) 。"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.084,
                0.511,
                0.923,
                0.691
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "2. 对 \\(k = 1, \\ldots, 100\\), 计算条件概率 \\(P(Y = y_{j} | X = x_{k}^{*})\\), 并记为 \\(p_{j \\mid k}^{*}\\) 。按照 \\(p_{j \\mid k}^{*}\\) 的概率从 \\(y_{j}\\) 中抽取壹个样本, 并记为 \\(y_{k}^{*}\\) 。"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "bbox": [
                0.085,
                0.736,
                0.605,
                0.808
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": "3. 样本 \\((x_{1}^{*}, y_{1}^{*}), \\ldots, (x_{100}^{*}, y_{100}^{*})\\) 即为所得。"
        },
        {
            "type": "list",
            "bbox": [
                0.084,
                0.294,
                0.923,
                0.808
            ],
            "angle": 0,
            "content": null
        }
    ],
